This Episode is brought you by Warhammer 40,000: Tacticus!  Tacticus is a turn-based tactical strategy game set in the eternal conflict of the  Warhammer 40,000 Universe.  Use Code PLAYON25 for 10 Isabel Shards and 2k Gold.  Valid until Dec 31st 2025 https://play.tacticusgame.com/playontt


Tyranid Hierophant Bio-Titan is the source of a rumbling threatening the entire planet. Worse yet it seems to be burrowed deep underground and attacking from 40mm tunnels. The Adepta Sororitas have been deployed to purge the threat. Jordan is back with Tyranids and has decided to try a Titan and Tak plays a new Sisters detachment.
